: .holiday file by Walter E Brown <wb@fnal.gov>
:
: Most country-specific contributions were taken from the plan
: distribution; their respective authors are credited below.
:
: The data herein have been organized into a standard format.  All
: countries' dates of interest have been grouped, and each entry is
: prefixed by a country (or, in a few cases, by a country_region) code.
: Each such code has a matching #define in Section 1; to enable a given
: collection of dates, #define the code to nothing; to disable a given
: collection of dates, #define the code to a colon (:).  As many codes
: as desired may be concurrently enabled.
